Male
(CAS). Total length 3.1 (3.3 with clypeus), carapace width 1.4. Leg 1: 33.2 (8.3 + 0.6 + 8.4 + 13.1, 2.8), tibia 2: 5.4, tibia 3: 3.9, tibia 4: 5.0; tibia 1 L/d: 63. Habitus as in 
