), tips 40 Mm apart. Palps as in 
Figures 238, 239
; trochanter with large retrolateral apophysis; femur proximo-dorsally with small apophysis; procursus with distal hinged process prolaterally; bulb with distinctive apophysis and membranous embolus (
Figs 238, 239
